data.enText: a plant with large green leaves that are eaten raw, especially in salad. There are many types of lettuce .

data.chText: 咸肉、生菜加番茄三明治
data.enText: a bacon, lettuce and tomato sandwich

data.chText: 买一个生菜和一些番茄。
data.enText: Buy a lettuce and some tomatoes.

tr: leaves of any of various plants of Lactuca sativa
any of various plants of the genus Lactuca

value.def: A lettuce is a plant with large green leaves that is the basic ingredient of many salads.

trans: 生菜；莴苣；长叶莴苣；罗蔓生菜；罗马生菜
